-- China to Speed Up Development of Energy-Saving Industry
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2013-07-12T13:31:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-12/china-to-speed-up-development-of-energy-saving-industry.html
China aims to speed up the
development of its energy-saving and environmental protection
industry, the State Council said in a  statement , citing a
Cabinet meeting at which Premier Li Keqiang presided.  The country will increase investment from its central
budget to support development of the energy-saving industry and
encourage the participation of private capital, according to the
statement posted on the State Councilâ€™s website.  Government and public-transportation vehicles should take
the lead in spreading the use of new-energy vehicles, according
to the statement  The Cabinet also called for more private sector investment
in the telecommunications industry and accelerated building and
upgrading of Internet and communications infrastructure. The
government will also push for the issue of 4G wireless licenses
within this year.  To contact Bloomberg News staff for this story:
